data.eml:eml: A collection of Sabellidae (Polychaeta) from Carrie Bow Cay (Belize, western Caribbean Sea) with the description of two new species

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Giangrande, Adriana, Licciano, Margherita, Gambi, Maria Cristina (2007): A collection of Sabellidae (Polychaeta) from Carrie Bow Cay (Belize, western Caribbean Sea) with the description of two new species. Zootaxa 1650: 41-53, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.179763
